text: Daniel Górak (born October 9, 1983) is a Polish table tennis player. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics as part of the Polish team in the men's team event. ==References== Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:Polish male table tennis players Category:Olympic table tennis players of Poland Category:Table tennis players at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Kraków Category:Table tennis players at the 2015 European Games Category:European Games competitors for Poland
